okja is a 2017 action-adventure film directed by bong joon-ho and co-written by bong and jon ronson . the film stars an ensemble cast headed by south korean child actress ahn seo-hyun , alongside hollywood actors tilda swinton , paul dano , steven yeun , lily collins , and jake gyllenhaal . the film competed for the palme d'or in the main competition section at the 2017 cannes film festival . it was released on netflix on june 28 , 2017 .